cs.CL, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV

This paper deals with natural language instructions for situated robotic tasks, which involves language understanding and spatial reasoning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also focuses on robotic tasks, which suggests the category cs.RO (Robotics and Control). The models presented in the paper involve machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper uses CNN-based models, which could also fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
